{"tid":1101252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武磊獲西班牙駕照！他能自己開車參加訓練","createTime":"2019-04-11T02:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T07:38:09.000Z","uid":1426,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"334810cccc80e69ee513acf92381925705f9d2b0","tid":1101252,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ottpsti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fottpsti.png&h=2edc6ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武磊能在巴塞隆拿當地開車　　據加泰羅尼亞媒體《世界體育報》的消息，武磊（W.Lei）獲得了他的西班牙駕照，他能自己開車去參加訓練。<br />\n自從1月底加盟愛斯賓奴之後，武磊迅速融入愛斯賓奴，如今他想去丹尼-哈爾克體育城，可以自行駕車前往。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvj79GJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvj79GJ.png&h=135118ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他的駕駛證通過了西班牙的驗證，獲準在巴塞隆拿開車。<br />\n《世界體育報》：武磊能在巴塞隆拿開車　　《世界體育報》指出，武磊如今在愛斯賓奴、在巴塞隆拿這座城市生活得很開心。他已經完美適應魯賓教練的體系。3月2日，愛斯賓奴與華拉度列的比賽，武磊成為西甲歷史上第一名取得入球的中國球員。"},{"pid":"8e8e5c2ded474933864209b93202c126921f1b6d","tid":1101252,"uid":1426,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"仆街copy 錯！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPtT5fh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPtT5fh.png&h=1ecf7c01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e92a4deb9f9240dcfbfda7f894847047db205ff1","tid":1101252,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb8024a7e1a584c4f809373cb557c8502e37e17","tid":1101252,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"武車王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebb3ac713e3a6cf66485530e8fceeba962156de","tid":1101252,"uid":37303,"like":3,"dislike